Extension registry operations

Usage: franken-node registry <COMMAND>

Commands:
  publish  Publish signed extension artifact
  search   Query extension registry with trust filters
  verify   Verify a locally stored registry artifact's hash and signature
  gc       Archive older locally stored registry artifacts, keeping the newest N active entries per lineage
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
